  "detailed_description": "<h1>Click the banner and join the Community!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Become the Super Villain.</strong></h2>Train in the simulation room to master your superpowers and prepare to Conquer Humanity.<br><br>Your superpowers not only include laser eyes but also flying, hyper speed dashes, super strength and a variety of range and melee attacks.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215060/extras/21d7f0966908a90b44f7c39c2e5de0be.poster.avif?t=1689338573\" width=720 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215060/extras/21d7f0966908a90b44f7c39c2e5de0be.webm?t=1689338573\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215060/extras/21d7f0966908a90b44f7c39c2e5de0be.mp4?t=1689338573\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215060/extras/1f16611be9e7624dbb0b469ea6ed222a.webp?t=1689338573\" width=618 height=21 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gore, Dismemberments and Destruction.</strong></h2>Master the combat and reach high <strong>Style Ranks</strong> by mixing up attacks and combos.<br><br>You are the strongest thing in the simulation, everything else can be destroyed, exploded or dismembered for those sweet slow motion moments.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215060/extras/91376ef5375514f1f7a8b959a18e622c.poster.avif?t=1689338573\" width=720 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215060/extras/91376ef5375514f1f7a8b959a18e622c.webm?t=1689338573\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215060/extras/91376ef5375514f1f7a8b959a18e622c.mp4?t=1689338573\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215060/extras/1f16611be9e7624dbb0b469ea6ed222a.webp?t=1689338573\" width=618 height=21 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Multiple enemies and Bosses.</strong></h2>Don't let your guard down, the simulation is filled with armed enemies and unique bosses.<br><br>Each boss has it's own weak points and tactics, practice their patterns to survive until the end.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215060/extras/37aa1a0e4110be012e9390253c464cc3.poster.avif?t=1689338573\" width=720 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215060/extras/37aa1a0e4110be012e9390253c464cc3.webm?t=1689338573\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215060/extras/37aa1a0e4110be012e9390253c464cc3.mp4?t=1689338573\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215060/extras/1f16611be9e7624dbb0b469ea6ed222a.webp?t=1689338573\" width=618 height=21 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WARNING:</strong> You thought you were good at games ? Think twice, this is actually difficult.</h2>If you're skilled, you can win the simulation without getting hit once but misjudging a move or not reacting fast enough can result in you being flatlined and disconnected out of the simulation.",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Become the Super Villain.</strong></h2>Train in the simulation room to master your superpowers and prepare to Conquer Humanity.<br><br>Your superpowers not only include laser eyes but also flying, hyper speed dashes, super strength and a variety of range and melee attacks.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215060/extras/21d7f0966908a90b44f7c39c2e5de0be.poster.avif?t=1689338573\" width=720 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215060/extras/21d7f0966908a90b44f7c39c2e5de0be.webm?t=1689338573\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215060/extras/21d7f0966908a90b44f7c39c2e5de0be.mp4?t=1689338573\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215060/extras/1f16611be9e7624dbb0b469ea6ed222a.webp?t=1689338573\" width=618 height=21 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gore, Dismemberments and Destruction.</strong></h2>Master the combat and reach high <strong>Style Ranks</strong> by mixing up attacks and combos.<br><br>You are the strongest thing in the simulation, everything else can be destroyed, exploded or dismembered for those sweet slow motion moments.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215060/extras/91376ef5375514f1f7a8b959a18e622c.poster.avif?t=1689338573\" width=720 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215060/extras/91376ef5375514f1f7a8b959a18e622c.webm?t=1689338573\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215060/extras/91376ef5375514f1f7a8b959a18e622c.mp4?t=1689338573\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215060/extras/1f16611be9e7624dbb0b469ea6ed222a.webp?t=1689338573\" width=618 height=21 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Multiple enemies and Bosses.</strong></h2>Don't let your guard down, the simulation is filled with armed enemies and unique bosses.<br><br>Each boss has it's own weak points and tactics, practice their patterns to survive until the end.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215060/extras/37aa1a0e4110be012e9390253c464cc3.poster.avif?t=1689338573\" width=720 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215060/extras/37aa1a0e4110be012e9390253c464cc3.webm?t=1689338573\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215060/extras/37aa1a0e4110be012e9390253c464cc3.mp4?t=1689338573\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215060/extras/1f16611be9e7624dbb0b469ea6ed222a.webp?t=1689338573\" width=618 height=21 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WARNING:</strong> You thought you were good at games ? Think twice, this is actually difficult.</h2>If you're skilled, you can win the simulation without getting hit once but misjudging a move or not reacting fast enough can result in you being flatlined and disconnected out of the simulation.",
